---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { DOWNLOAD_URL, GITHUB_REPO_URL, ZIP_DOWNLOAD_URL } from "../config";
import type { Locale } from "../lib/i18n";

const { locale } = Astro.props as { locale: Locale };
const description =
  locale === "zh"
    ? "下载适用于 Apple 芯片 Mac 的最新版 Codex Themes，并查看 Codex 版本要求、更新与首次安装说明。"
    : "Download the latest Codex Themes for Apple silicon Macs and review Codex version, update, and first-run guidance.";
---

<BaseLayout locale={locale} title={locale === "zh" ? "下载" : "Download"} description={description}>
  <section class="download-page-hero section-shell">
    <div class="eyebrow">CODEX THEMES · LATEST BETA</div>
    <h1>{locale === "zh" ? "下载，然后打开一个更有趣的 Codex。" : "Download a more personal Codex workspace."}</h1>
    <p>{description}</p>
    <div class="download-card">
      <div class="download-card-main">
        <div class="platform-mark">macOS</div>
        <div>
          <h2>{locale === "zh" ? "Apple 芯片版" : "Apple silicon"}</h2>
          <p>M1 / M2 / M3 / M4 · macOS 13+</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="download-card-actions">
        <a class="button button-blue" href={DOWNLOAD_URL}>{locale === "zh" ? "下载 DMG" : "Download DMG"}</a>
        <a class="text-link" href={ZIP_DOWNLOAD_URL}>{locale === "zh" ? "下载 ZIP" : "Download ZIP"}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="availability-note">
      {locale === "zh"
        ? "Intel Mac 与 Windows 暂不支持，我们不会提供无法使用的安装包。"
        : "Intel Mac and Windows are not supported yet, so we do not offer non-working downloads."}
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="install-guide section-shell">
    <div class="section-kicker">{locale === "zh" ? "安装与更新" : "INSTALL & UPDATE"}</div>
    <div class="install-guide-grid">
      <h2>
        {locale === "zh"
          ? "先把 Codex 和 Codex Themes 都更新到最新版"
          : "Keep both Codex and Codex Themes up to date"}
      </h2>
      <div>
        <ol>
          <li>
            {locale === "zh"
              ? "先从官方渠道安装或升级到最新版 ChatGPT / Codex 桌面应用，并确认可以进入 Codex 模式。"
              : "First install or update the official ChatGPT / Codex desktop app and confirm that Codex mode is available."}
          </li>
          <li>
            {locale === "zh"
              ? "从本页面下载最新版 Codex Themes；不要继续使用旧安装包。"
              : "Download the latest Codex Themes from this page instead of reusing an older installer."}
          </li>
          <li>{locale === "zh" ? "打开 DMG，把 Codex Themes 拖入“应用程序”。" : "Open the DMG and drag Codex Themes into Applications."}</li>
          <li>{locale === "zh" ? "第一次打开若被阻止，进入“系统设置 → 隐私与安全性”，选择“仍要打开”。" : "If the first launch is blocked, open System Settings → Privacy & Security and choose Open Anyway."}</li>
          <li>
            {locale === "zh"
              ? "以后看到客户端更新提示请及时升级；若自动安装受 macOS 限制，请重新下载最新版 DMG 覆盖安装。"
              : "Install future in-app updates promptly. If macOS blocks automatic installation, download the latest DMG and install it over the existing copy."}
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          {locale === "zh"
            ? "Codex 界面会持续迭代，Codex Themes 也会同步提供兼容修复。遇到主题显示异常时，请先确认两边都是最新版，再重新应用主题。应用不修改 Codex 安装包，也不会读取 API Key。"
            : "Codex evolves continuously, and Codex Themes ships matching compatibility fixes. If a theme looks wrong, update both apps first and reapply the theme. Codex Themes does not patch Codex or read API keys."}
        </p>
        <aside class="install-troubleshooting">
          <h3>
            {locale === "zh"
              ? "提示“Codex Themes.app 已损坏”怎么办"
              : "If macOS says Codex Themes.app is damaged"}
          </h3>
          <p>
            {locale === "zh"
              ? "当前安装包尚未完成 Apple 签名与公证。浏览器下载后，macOS 会添加 com.apple.quarantine 隔离属性；Gatekeeper 无法验证开发者身份时，有时会把应用显示为“已损坏”。这通常是隔离策略造成的拦截，并不代表文件真的损坏。"
              : "The current build is not yet Apple-signed or notarized. macOS adds the com.apple.quarantine attribute to browser downloads, and Gatekeeper may report an unverified app as damaged. This is usually a quarantine block rather than actual file corruption."}
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>
              {locale === "zh"
                ? "确认 DMG 来自本官网或官方 GitHub Release，把最新版 Codex Themes.app 拖入“应用程序”并覆盖旧版本。"
                : "Confirm the DMG came from this website or the official GitHub Release, then copy the latest Codex Themes.app to Applications and replace the old copy."}
            </li>
            <li>
              {locale === "zh"
                ? "打开“终端”，执行下面的命令。"
                : "Open Terminal and run the command below."}
            </li>
          </ol>
          <pre><code>xattr -dr com.apple.quarantine "/Applications/Codex Themes.app"</code></pre>
          <p>
            {locale === "zh"
              ? "然后重新打开应用。这条命令只移除 Codex Themes 的下载隔离属性，不会全局关闭 Gatekeeper；请勿对来源不明的应用执行。"
              : "Then reopen the app. This removes quarantine only from Codex Themes and does not disable Gatekeeper globally. Never run it for an app from an untrusted source."}
          </p>
        </aside>
        <a class="text-link" href={GITHUB_REPO_URL}>{locale === "zh" ? "在 GitHub 查看源码" : "View the source on GitHub"}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
